==English==

===Etymology===
''[[ultra]]-'' prefix from Latin: "beyond" + ''[[telluric]]'': pertaining to the earth

===Adjective===
'''ultratelluric'''
([[science fiction]] or [[fantasy]] [[jargon]])
# Coming from outside the Earth.
#:''"...among the Records stolen from the Gods were certain tablets of '''ultratelluric''' stone...''" ("Papyrus of the Dark Wisdom", [[Wikipedia:Lin Carter|Lin Carter]]).
# [[unearthly|Unearthly]].
# [[extraterrestrial|Extraterrestrial]].